:FED.
13. Changes to the rules
:SKRSLUT.
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
Changes to the rules as well as the schedule of fees are subject to two
months' notice if the change is to the detriment of the account holder and
user. Changes to the advantage of the account holder and user may be made
without notice. Changes will be notified by paper or by electronic
notification, e.g. by text message. The user/account holder must notify
&BANKNAVN. of any address or email changes, and the user/account holder
is responsible for not receiving notifications on changes if no such email
or address changes have been notified.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Any changes to rules will be considered accepted unless the user/account
holder notifies &BANKNAVN. prior to the date of commencement that the
user/account holder does not wish to be bound by the new rules.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the user/account holder does not wish to be bound by the new rules, the
agreement will terminate at the time of commencement of the new rules. Any
prepaid fees will be refunded proportionately.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
