15. Use, storage and disclosure of information
.hy on
:SKRSLUT.
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
When payment is made using Mobile Money, the mobile number registered will
be recorded along with the transaction identification, amount, date of
transaction, where Mobile Money was used as well as the data for use for
the transaction identification. Information is stored with the shop, with
&BANKNAVN. and with &NETS. and will also be available to the account
holder in &WEBSYSNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The information is used by &BANKNAVN. for bookkeeping purposes, bank
statements and subsequent corrections of errors, if any.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The information is disclosed to others only if required by Danish law or
if needed for legal proceedings arising out of the use of Mobile Money.
.sp 3mm
The information is stored pursuant to applicable law.
